FROM (
  SELECT p.hospitalid,
         SUM(c.cost) AS total_cost
  FROM cost c

);

  AND strftime('%m', d_an.diagnosistime) = strftime('%m', d_gi.diagnosistime)
  AND d_an.diagnosistime > d_gi.diagnosistime;

  frequency DESC

  prescription_count desc
